document_data.Relationships:
Myrmeen was married twice in her life, first to a man named [[Dak]] in [[Calimshan]], and later to [[Haverstrom Lhal]], cousin to King [[Azoun IV]] of [[Cormyr]]. [[Krystin]], her adopted [[Calishite]] daughter;{{Cite dungeon/198/Cormyr Royale: The Royal Court of the Forest Kingdom|47-48}}

The Lady Lord was served by [[Evon Stralana]], Arabel's minister of defense.

Her former traveling companion [[Elyn]] remained a good friend throughout her years as a ruler, often aiding her when she continued embarking on adventurers incognito.
